text: The Lamborghini Murciélago is a supercar. Lamborghini built it from 2001 to 2010. The Murciélago was succeeded by the Lamborghini Aventador. It replaced the Diablo. The Murciélago was designed by Luc Donckerwolke. Lamborghini built 4,099 Murciélagos. ==References== Murcielago Category:Coupes Category:Roadsters Category:Sports cars Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles
